channel.description: GamingAngels.com is the premier online community for women to talk about all things geek! We'll feature guests from the various industries and talk with you in the chat room to get your opinions.

item.title: GamingAngels Game Chat - Jan 15,2009
item.description:
First we reported on what is going on in the world of all things GA. Next we spoke about the latest blogs and why Japanese companies feel the need to "westernize". I ran through Game News and ranted a bit on Game Politics. Look for me to bring more politics into our casts. You all are smart enough, it's time to take some action. We cover anime news and talk about cosplay in Australia. Pinksage takes over with awesome comic coverage. Talking about what's new and what you have to get. I spent a few minutes talking about CES and the lack of extra time we had.
